<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouveau RDV confirm√© - Recyclum</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f8fa;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.02) 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .alert-box .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .alert-box h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #1a2332;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        .alert-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c7783;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .info-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .info-item .label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6c7783;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .info-item .value {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #1a2332;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .client-box {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #e6edf2;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .client-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #1a2332;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        .client-detail {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .client-detail:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .client-detail .icon {
            width: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #3b82f6;
        }
        .client-detail .text {
            color: #1a2332;
        }
        .problem-box {
            background: #fff9e6;
            border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .problem-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        .problem-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white !important;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-container {
            text-align: center;
        }
        hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e6edf2;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üîî Nouveau rendez-vous confirm√©</h1>
        <p>Un client a confirm√© sa prise de rendez-vous</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="alert-box">
            <div class="icon">üìÖ</div>
            <h2>{{ appointment.dateFormatted }}</h2>
            <p>√† {{ appointment.appointmentTime|date('H:i') }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="label">N¬∞ Demande</div>
                <div class="value">#{{ request.id }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="label">Type</div>
                <div class="value">{{ request.repairLocationLabel }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="label">Appareil</div>
                <div class="value">{{ request.categoryLabel }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="label">Confirm√© le</div>
                <div class="value">{{ appointment.confirmedAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="client-box">
            <h3>üë§ Informations client</h3>
            <div class="client-detail">
                <div class="icon">üë§</div>
                <div class="text"><strong>{{ request.fullName }}</strong></div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-detail">
                <div class="icon">üìß</div>
                <div class="text">{{ request.email }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-detail">
                <div class="icon">üìû</div>
                <div class="text">{{ request.phone }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-detail">
                <div class="icon">üìç</div>
                <div class="text">{{ request.fullAddress }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="client-box">
            <h3>üîß D√©tails de l'appareil</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #1a2332; line-height: 1.6;">
                <strong>Cat√©gorie :</strong> {{ request.categoryLabel }}<br>
                {% if request.brand %}<strong>Marque :</strong> {{ request.brand }}{% if request.model %} {{ request.model }}{% endif %}<br>{% endif %}
                {% if request.urgency %}<strong style="color: #ef4444;">‚ö†Ô∏è URGENT</strong><br>{% endif %}
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="problem-box">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Probl√®me signal√©</h3>
            <p><strong>{{ request.issue }}</strong></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">{{ request.issueDetails }}</p>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <div class="cta-container">
            <a href="{{ viewUrl }}" class="cta-button">
                üëÅÔ∏è Voir la demande compl√®te
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; color: #6c7783; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
            N'oubliez pas de contacter le client 24h avant l'intervention pour confirmer le rendez-vous.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
